2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper mentions the use of deep learning techniques for achieving high accuracy on real-world datasets. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with the development of a tool for generating realistic raw images of printed photographs. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with image processing and color correction techniques. 
5. cs.GR (Graphics) is also a possible category as the paper deals with the generation of realistic images of printed photographs.
